attributes.Long form description: The student begins to assemble the table, first assembling the two legs of the table with the shelf and then screwing them together with the Allen wrench. Once the screws are in place, the student has to assemble the other two legs of the table to finally place the top and finish with the assembled table.

attributes.Transcription: We will now assemble a bedside table from Ikea, please go ahead and assemble it.

attributes.Action sentence: The student screws the fist leg to the shelf.
The student screws the second leg to the shelf.
The student screws the third leg to the shelf.
The student screws the fourth leg to the shelf.
The student screws the left leg to the table.
The student screws the opposite leg to the table.
The student screws the back left leg to the table.
The student screws the front right leg to the table.
